#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/community/_index.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Community"
msgstr "Komunitas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:7
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Whether it be to solve a problem or to contribute in any way, the Xfce "
"communities are a good place to get help or to share your ideas. You might "
"also want to have a look at the communities of the different distributions "
"which provide Xfce.\n"
msgstr ""
"Baik itu untuk memecahkan persoalan atau berkontribusi dalam cara apapun, "
"komunitas Xfce adalah tempat yang bagus untuk mendapatkan bantuan atau "
"berbagi ide Anda. Anda mungkin ingin juga melihat komunitas distribusi yang "
"berbeda yang juga menyediakan Xfce.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/community/_index.md:8
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "Mailing lists"
msgstr "Milis"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:11
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Almost all development and coordination work is taking place on the Xfce "
"mailing lists. A summary of all lists is available at "
"[mail.xfce.org](https://mail.xfce.org). There is also a user-specific list "
"where you can ask questions and freely discuss about the desktop.\n"
msgstr ""
"Hampir semua pekerjaan pengembangan dan koordinasi dilakukan di milis Xfce. "
"Daftar semua milis tersedia di [mail.xfce.org](https://mail.xfce.org). Ada "
"juga daftar khusus pengguna tempat Anda dapat bertanya dan bebas berdiskusi "
"seputar desktop.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:13
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "**NOTE**: In order to post to these lists, you must first subscribe.\n"
msgstr ""
"**CATATAN**: Agar dapat melakukan pos di milis ini, Anda harus berlangganan "
"terlebih dahulu.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/community/_index.md:14
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "Matrix"
msgstr "Matrix"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:17
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If you have a problem that you cannot resolve, you might want to try asking "
"a question in our Matrix channel "
"[#xfce](https://matrix.to/#/#xfce:matrix.org). The channel has several "
"active users. It is recommended that you consult the "
"[documentation](https://docs.xfce.org/) about your problem before asking "
"your question.\n"
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda memiliki masalah yang tidak dapat Anda atasi, Anda mungkin ingin "
"mencoba mengajukan pertanyaan di saluran Matrix kami <a "
"href=\\\"https://matrix.to/#/#xfce:matrix.org\\\">#xfce</a>. Saluran ini "
"memiliki beberapa pengguna aktif. Disarankan agar Anda merujuk ke <a "
"href=\\\"https://docs.xfce.org/\\\" class=\\\"external\\\">dokumentasi</a> "
"mengenai masalah Anda sebelum mengajukan pertanyaan.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/community/_index.md:18
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "Forums"
msgstr "Forum"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:21
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"For users who prefer forums, the [Xfce Forum](https://forum.xfce.org/) is "
"the place to be. Active contributors will be able to help you, but please do"
" not use it for bug reports.\n"
msgstr ""
"Bagi pengguna yang lebih menyukai forum, [Forum "
"Xfce](https://forum.xfce.org/) adalah tempat yang tepat. Kontributor aktif "
"bisa membantu Anda, tetapi mohon jangan menggunakannya untuk melaporkan "
"kutu.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/community/_index.md:22
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "Social Networks"
msgstr "Social Network"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:24
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You can follow us on the official [Mastodon "
"account](https://floss.social/@xfce) or [Twitter "
"account](https://twitter.com/xfceofficial)\n"
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mengikuti kami di <a href=\\\"https://floss.social/@xfce\\\" "
"class=\\\"external\\\">akun Mastodon</a> resmi atau <a "
"href=\\\"https://twitter.com/xfceofficial\\\" class=\\\"external\\\">akun "
"Twitter</a>\n"
